      <title><![CDATA[Cold Pig]]></title>
      <url>http://coldpig.me/2016/12/12/Cold-Pig/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Cold pig: 啥意思呢？“冷猪”吗？用脚趾头想都知道这不是正确答案。</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<p> 看看解释吧：</p>
<blockquote>
<p>To give cold pig is a punishment inflicted on sluggards who lie too long in bed: it consists in pulling off all the bed clothes from them, and throwing cold water upon them.<br> 简单说来就是以一种粗暴的方法把睡懒觉的人弄醒。</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
